00:35:20,300 --> 00:35:21,770
Have some duck.

529
00:35:30,270 --> 00:35:31,670
Here.

530
00:35:37,170 --> 00:35:39,000
Han Li!

531
00:35:39,000 --> 00:35:40,700
Han Li?

532
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:46,740
Why are you out here? Go in now!

533
00:35:49,190 --> 00:35:50,510
What are you doing?

534
00:35:50,510 --> 00:35:52,090
What's wrong?

535
00:35:56,900 --> 00:35:58,090
You fool!

536
00:35:58,090 --> 00:36:00,780
What's the biggest taboo for cultivators?

537
00:36:00,780 --> 00:36:05,220
They must avoid impure food like meat and wine.

538
00:36:05,220 --> 00:36:12,090
It means this boy has reached Level Two!

539
00:36:13,410 --> 00:36:15,907
Level Two?

540
00:36:15,907 --> 00:36:19,030
He has set foot on the immortal path!

541
00:36:20,560 --> 00:36:23,050
Really?

542
00:36:23,050 --> 00:36:24,450
From now on,

543
00:36:24,450 --> 00:36:31,380
he'll be entirely different from mere mortals like you!

544
00:36:46,380 --> 00:36:50,760
 This year, I broke through Level Two of my chant training. 

545
00:36:51,378 --> 00:36:53,050
 Master kept his promise. 

546
00:36:53,050 --> 00:36:55,070
 He taught me medical skills, 

547
00:36:56,280 --> 00:37:00,130
 refinement of medicines, herb preparation, acupuncture. 

548
00:37:00,130 --> 00:37:02,700
 He taught me everything without reservation. 

549
00:37:02,700 --> 00:37:08,480
 Right now, even my monthly allowance has more than doubled. 

550
00:37:09,220 --> 00:37:12,410
 I wonder how everyone in the village is doing. 

551
00:37:12,410 --> 00:37:16,240
 Father, Mother, and Xiaomei. 

552
00:37:16,240 --> 00:37:19,410
 I'm doing well here. 

553
00:37:19,410 --> 00:37:21,460
 You don't need to worry about me. 

554
00:37:23,510 --> 00:37:25,900
 Apart from taking care of our daily meals and needs, 

555
00:37:25,900 --> 00:37:27,250
 Zhang Tie spent the rest of his time 

556
00:37:27,250 --> 00:37:29,660
 practicing a technique called the Elephant Armor Technique 

557
00:37:29,660 --> 00:37:31,316
 which Master has imparted to him. 

558
00:37:31,316 --> 00:37:33,340
 I don't see any bronze muscles or iron bones. 

559
00:37:33,340 --> 00:37:37,040
 Being covered in cuts and bruises became the norm instead. 

560
00:37:37,040 --> 00:37:38,360
 Using the medical skills that I've learned, 

561
00:37:38,360 --> 00:37:40,180
 I created medicines to heal his injuries. 

562
00:37:40,180 --> 00:37:43,840
 At least I can finally help to relieve some of his pain. 

563
00:37:46,710 --> 00:37:48,670
 After reaching Level Two, 

564
00:37:48,670 --> 00:37:50,530
 I realize that I can see even further. 

565
00:37:50,530 --> 00:37:52,220
 My hearing is clearer, too. 

566
00:37:52,220 --> 00:37:55,090
 My mind has become a bit sharper, as well. 

567
00:37:55,090 --> 00:37:59,100
 Seems like there's something magical about the chant indeed. 

568
00:38:00,760 --> 00:38:04,450
 Back then, Li Feiyu, who led us into the sect, 

569
00:38:04,450 --> 00:38:05,978
 also known as Senior Brother Li, 

570
00:38:05,978 --> 00:38:07,900
 was also promoted from an ordinary steward 

571
00:38:07,900 --> 00:38:10,670
 to the Deputy Hall Master of Outer Blade Hall. 

572
00:38:10,670 --> 00:38:12,930
 He deals with the villainous and wicked bandit gang 

573
00:38:12,930 --> 00:38:14,680
 called the Wild Wolves Gang. 

574
00:38:15,630 --> 00:38:17,536
 I was once very envious of him. 

575
00:38:17,536 --> 00:38:19,300
 I wanted to be like him. 

576
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:23,030
 I wanted to train to become a martial arts expert and be a chivalrous hero. 

577
00:38:23,030 --> 00:38:24,710
 I wanted to roam the world, 

578
00:38:24,710 --> 00:38:27,690
 take revenge and repay gratitude swiftly. 

579
00:38:27,690 --> 00:38:31,400
 A pity there are no "what ifs" in life. 

580
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:35,380
 I could only practice daily and consume herbal medicines. 

581
00:38:35,380 --> 00:38:40,800
 Unknowingly, that thought seems to have faded. 

582
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:02,270
Scram!

583
00:39:09,360 --> 00:39:11,710
Tell the entire Wild Wolves Gang

584
00:39:11,710 --> 00:39:15,230
to stop dreaming of stepping into the Seven Mystics Sect.

585
00:39:15,230 --> 00:39:16,850
Otherwise,

586
00:39:17,960 --> 00:39:19,900
you will end up like this.

587
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:22,910
 Let's go! 

588
00:39:32,030 --> 00:39:34,230
Master, look at the gardenias. 
    

589
00:39:34,230 --> 00:39:35,780
They're growing so well.

590
00:39:35,780 --> 00:39:37,600
If we boil them

591
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:40,731
and mix them with powdered licorice root to make Duanmu tofu,

592
00:39:40,731 --> 00:39:43,461
it'll turn into a top-notch vegetarian dish.

593
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:47,910
Child, plants are not the only edible food around here.

594
00:39:47,910 --> 00:39:51,130
In this vast world, even stones and sand,

595
00:39:51,130 --> 00:39:52,970
dew at dawn and glow at dusk,

596
00:39:52,970 --> 00:39:55,524
can serve as sustenance.

597
00:39:55,524 --> 00:39:57,490
Lately,

598
00:39:57,490 --> 00:40:01,050
I've been thinking about the chant that you taught me.

599
00:40:02,439 --> 00:40:04,130
Tell me what's on your mind.

600
00:40:04,130 --> 00:40:05,660
Attain ultimate emptiness.

601
00:40:05,660 --> 00:40:07,230
Maintain profound tranquility.

602
00:40:07,230 --> 00:40:11,700
Maybe it's because nothing is perfect in the world.

603
00:40:12,800 --> 00:40:17,420
Due to the imperfection, mortals feel empty and lost.

604
00:40:18,110 --> 00:40:21,000
Only by accepting such emptiness,

605
00:40:21,000 --> 00:40:24,090
we will be able to find tranquility.

606
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:32,460
Did I say something wrong?

607
00:40:33,880 --> 00:40:36,030
From now on, you're only allowed to gather herbs.

608
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:40,480
Do not read any books again.

609
00:40:40,480 --> 00:40:42,170
Why?

610
00:40:43,710 --> 00:40:46,660
Your cultivation speed has been too slow for the past few months.

611
00:40:46,660 --> 00:40:48,670
Focus on your cultivation.

612
00:40:48,670 --> 00:40:52,480
Other matters have nothing to do with you.

613
00:41:05,000 --> 00:41:07,320
It's all your fault!

614
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:10,281
Who told you to let him read books?

615
00:41:10,281 --> 00:41:12,402
He now has his own opinions.

616
00:41:12,402 --> 00:41:13,597
How can we control him like this?

617
00:41:13,597 --> 00:41:15,670
Shut up!

618
00:41:15,670 --> 00:41:19,520
If I didn't use medical skills to entice him to stay in this valley,

619
00:41:19,520 --> 00:41:22,650
would he have focused on his cultivation?

620
00:41:26,880 --> 00:41:29,550
You're pathetic.

621
00:41:29,550 --> 00:41:32,830
You only know how to nag at people nonstop.

622
00:41:34,670 --> 00:41:36,000
If you have that much time,

623
00:41:36,000 --> 00:41:39,260
you should keep a close eye on that child.

624
00:41:48,190 --> 00:41:50,510
 Master took all the books away. 

625
00:41:50,510 --> 00:41:52,400
 He replaced them with herbs. 

626
00:41:55,070 --> 00:41:58,875
 Why is Master's mood so unpredictable? 

627
00:41:58,875 --> 00:42:01,180
 It's like he has suddenly turned into a different person. 

628
00:42:01,180 --> 00:42:03,200
 I must be careful in the future. 

629
00:42:03,200 --> 00:42:06,330
 I must not let people read my mind that easily. 

630
00:42:28,150 --> 00:42:30,380
 That chant brought me into Level Two of cultivation. 

631
00:42:30,380 --> 00:42:32,880
 This situation has never happened in the past. 

632
00:42:32,880 --> 00:42:37,310
 I keep feeling that something bad is about to happen. 

633
00:42:38,710 --> 00:42:40,220
 What is this? 

634
00:42:47,840 --> 00:42:51,760
 Why is this vial glowing? 

635
00:42:57,920 --> 00:43:00,360
 It can absorb moonlight? 

636
00:43:20,200 --> 00:43:22,780
 Seems like my hypothesis was correct. 

637
00:43:22,780 --> 00:43:24,000
 The closed door and windows 

638
00:43:24,000 --> 00:43:26,930
 were obstructing the vial from absorbing the rays of light. 

639
00:43:26,930 --> 00:43:29,090
 The vial can absorb the rays of light better 

640
00:43:29,090 --> 00:43:31,480
 in spacious areas with open space. 

641
00:43:31,480 --> 00:43:35,030
 Only then will the light orb be larger. 

642
00:43:35,030 --> 00:43:38,380
 Although I don't know where the rays of light are coming from 

643
00:43:38,380 --> 00:43:42,080
 or what the usage of the vial is when it absorbs the rays of light, 

644
00:43:42,080 --> 00:43:45,940
 but I should be getting closer to solving the puzzle. 

645
00:43:46,630 --> 00:43:49,330
 But why can't I open it? 

646
00:43:59,630 --> 00:44:00,880
Why are you only here now?

647
00:44:00,880 --> 00:44:03,150
Aren't we supposed to meet at the 3rd quarter of the Hour of Yin*? 
  (*Around 3:45 a.m.) 

648
00:44:03,150 --> 00:44:04,900
Li Feiyu is doing his rounds tonight.

649
00:44:04,900 --> 00:44:06,700
I'm lucky that I'm able to be here.

650
00:44:06,700 --> 00:44:07,740
 Is that a member of the Wild Wolves Gang 

651
00:44:07,740 --> 00:44:09,740
 and a member of the Seven Mystics Sect? 

652
00:44:09,740 --> 00:44:12,860
Did you find any news about that batch of goods?

653
00:44:12,860 --> 00:44:14,150
Of course.

654
00:44:14,150 --> 00:44:16,450
This is a birthday gift for the prince's residence.

655
00:44:16,450 --> 00:44:18,320
 He's actually colluding with the Wild Wolves Gang 

656
00:44:18,320 --> 00:44:20,030
 and betrayed the Seven Mystics Sect. 

657
00:44:20,030 --> 00:44:21,360
 I must rush back to report this. 

658
00:44:21,360 --> 00:44:23,080
We'll depart in three days.

659
00:44:23,080 --> 00:44:24,260
How much can we rob from them this time?

660
00:44:24,260 --> 00:44:25,620
Who's there?

661
00:44:30,280 --> 00:44:31,480
You should return first.

662
00:44:31,480 --> 00:44:33,000
Don't let people see us together. 
   

663
00:44:33,000 --> 00:44:34,560
I'll go after him.

664
00:44:45,480 --> 00:44:47,960
You don't know martial arts, but you can run fast.

665
00:45:01,110 --> 00:45:02,650
Master?

666
00:45:05,190 --> 00:45:07,820
I told you to focus on your cultivation in the valley.

667
00:45:07,820 --> 00:45:10,010
Why did you get into a fight with him here?

668
00:45:10,010 --> 00:45:12,720
Master, I couldn't sleep last night

669
00:45:12,720 --> 00:45:14,010
and came to the forest to practice.

670
00:45:14,010 --> 00:45:16,840
I accidentally overheard about his collusion with the Wild Wolves Gang.

671
00:45:16,840 --> 00:45:17,970
He betrayed the Seven Mystics Sect!

672
00:45:17,970 --> 00:45:19,660
What Seven Mystics Sect?

673
00:45:19,660 --> 00:45:20,780
What Wild Wolves Gang?

674
00:45:20,780 --> 00:45:22,180
The mortals can fight and betray each other.

675
00:45:22,180 --> 00:45:24,050
That's none of your business.

676
00:45:24,050 --> 00:45:25,900
Do you know that your life

677
00:45:25,900 --> 00:45:29,340
is more precious than the entire Seven Mystics Sect?

678
00:45:38,510 --> 00:45:43,140
I won't let anyone harm you.

679
00:45:44,030 --> 00:45:45,190
He's a mole.

680
00:45:45,190 --> 00:45:48,570
Did you not hear me?

681
00:45:51,150 --> 00:45:52,970
Go back and focus on your cultivation.

682
00:45:52,970 --> 00:45:55,850
Reach Level Three as soon as possible.

683
00:46:01,150 --> 00:46:05,888
You scoundrels have never shown me any respect.

684
00:46:05,888 --> 00:46:06,970
Do you think

685
00:46:06,970 --> 00:46:10,780
I'm old, deaf, and blind?

686
00:46:10,780 --> 00:46:13,880
Do you know who his life belongs to?

687
00:46:15,760 --> 00:46:20,972
No one can touch a strand of his hair, except me!

688
00:46:39,520 --> 00:46:40,930
Han Li! Something bad has happened!

689
00:46:40,930 --> 00:46:44,310
A member of the Seven Mystics Sect fell off the mountain!

690
00:46:45,760 --> 00:46:47,570
Master killed him.

691
00:46:51,880 --> 00:46:53,330
Master...

692
00:46:58,550 --> 00:46:59,820
Master?

693
00:46:59,820 --> 00:47:01,570
It can't be.

694
00:47:03,190 --> 00:47:05,390
Master killed someone!

695
00:47:06,400 --> 00:47:09,530
Master killed someone?

696
00:47:21,680 --> 00:47:26,240
 Master is actually a hidden martial arts expert. 

697
00:47:26,240 --> 00:47:29,300
 Why hasn't he shown his skills in front of us? 

698
00:47:29,300 --> 00:47:31,740
 Did he deliberately hide it, 

699
00:47:31,740 --> 00:47:33,390
 or... 

700
00:47:42,710 --> 00:47:45,608
How can you cultivate in peace

701
00:47:45,608 --> 00:47:48,800
when your heart is so restless?

702
00:47:48,800 --> 00:47:51,700
You've been slacking off too much lately.

703
00:47:53,150 --> 00:47:54,510
It's raining heavily out there.

704
00:47:54,510 --> 00:47:56,530
Sleep early.

705
00:47:56,530 --> 00:47:57,960
Once the weather has cleared,

706
00:47:57,960 --> 00:48:01,670
I'll descend the mountain to seek medicine for you.

707
00:48:01,670 --> 00:48:03,330
Remember.

708
00:48:04,880 --> 00:48:08,760
I'll always keep an eye on you.

